body_html:
I found that this happens with tensorflow v1.8 (installed by default with !pip3 install --quiet --upgrade --pre tensorflow)

Changing to
!pip3 install --quiet tensorflow==1.7
allows
embed = hub.Module("https://tfhub.dev/google/universal-sentence-encoder/1")
to execute successfully.

body:
I found that this happens with tensorflow v1.8 (installed by default with `!pip3 install --quiet --upgrade --pre tensorflow`)

Changing to 
`!pip3 install --quiet tensorflow==1.7` 
allows 
`embed = hub.Module("https://tfhub.dev/google/universal-sentence-encoder/1")` 
to execute successfully.
